        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-23" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,1,0&quot;&gt;Atletas / Encarregados de Educação (Submissão) e Gerência (Validação)&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-24" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;O sistema deve permitir o registo autónomo de lesões ou queixas físicas por parte do atleta. Esta ação cria&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;automaticamente um alerta clínico, integrando o atleta numa &quot;zona de lesionados&quot; visível para a equipa técnica&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;e para o departamento médico, que fará o acompanhamento até à respetiva alta.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="1260" x="491" y="-340" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
